546
00:38:23.551 --> 00:38:24.802  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Say the name, Rodrigo.

547
00:38:27.305 --> 00:38:28.347  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[sighs]

548
00:38:29.557 --> 00:38:30.766  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Escobar.

549
00:38:36.480 --> 00:38:40.401  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Don't look at me like that, Horacio.
I've always cared for you.

550
00:38:40.484 --> 00:38:44.864  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
